  <brief_title>REsearching Coronary REduction by Appropriately Targeting Euglycemia (RECREATE Pilot Study)</brief_title>
  <acronym>RECREATE Pilot</acronym>
  <official_title>An International Multicentre Randomized Controlled Trial of Intensive Insulin Therapy Targeting Normoglycemia In Acute Myocardial Infarction: the RECREATE (REsearching Coronary REduction by Appropriately Targeting Euglycemia) Pilot Study</official_title>
